				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/C%E1%BB%95-du%E1%BB%87-t%E1%BB%AB-t%E1%BB%B1-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-y1DEERPb1foNOuYfDE3Leg">Cổ duệ từ tự tự - 鼓枻詞自序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/H%E1%BB%93i-Nh%E1%BA%A1n-phong/poem-r2iQKT6YFl5-dxf_RUVV2Q">Hồi Nhạn phong - 回鴈峰</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/author-n8TXz8ZnEQ2g7U6IvK74Vw">Nguyễn Trung Ngạn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Kh%E1%BB%91c-Vi-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-phu-Chi-T%E1%BA%A5n/poem-MtT3Ty8giRzakCI6V8vRQQ">Khốc Vi đại phu Chi Tấn - 哭韋大夫之晉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Mai-Nghi%C3%AAu-Th%E1%BA%A7n/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nhi%C3%AAu-Ch%C3%A2u-to%E1%BA%A1-trung-kh%C3%A1ch-ng%E1%BB%AF-th%E1%BB%B1c-h%C3%A0-%C4%91%E1%BB%93n-ng%C6%B0/poem-s9YL-mFZgyycLmYcfJnfUQ">Phạm Nhiêu Châu toạ trung khách ngữ thực hà đồn ngư - 范饒州坐中客語食河豚魚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Mai-Nghi%C3%AAu-Th%E1%BA%A7n/author-LM0kb8TnwF3pXyZ2viD2Eg">Mai Nghiêu Thần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Quan-th%C6%B0-3/poem-0CTnEDQGEKViETWZXrhgww">Quan thư 3 - 關雎 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Chu/T%C3%A2y-s%C6%A1n-h%E1%BB%AFu-h%E1%BB%95-h%C3%A0nh/poem-oKK18x5fVSeXLcS3AA-9aw">Tây sơn hữu hổ hành - 西山有虎行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Chu/author-FLEf_-t0yNozAM5JmBQyAg">Thẩm Chu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Ch%C3%BA/T%C3%A2y-Thi/poem-pk_M_GOJPdTfY-ncAU5Fdw">Tây Thi - 西施</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Ch%C3%BA/author-VHS_JvG4NANbuv3vgzgaQQ">Lư Chú</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Tr%E1%BA%A1o-ca-thanh/poem-pFSgQN-tjw3hMC3siNzEpQ">Trạo ca thanh - 棹歌聲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-PBy92bBuBMMs53v9tc9E0A">Hồ Xuân Hương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/Tr%C3%A2n-ch%C3%A2u-li%C3%AAm/poem-oesM_lFSGx5pSn8Iok7DRQ">Trân châu liêm - 真珠簾</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-c%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-nNk4C1iEfhXLc6tjiK7Ekg">Vịnh cúc kỳ 2 - 詠菊其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
